                                            "imageName":  "WraithReap.png"
                                        },
                                        {
                                            "name":  "Sow",
                                            "description":  "Plant a death seed in nearby targets to drain their lifeforce. Reap what has been sown to detonate afflicted enemies, dealing a percentage of their health as radial damage. The souls of the dead fill the Death Well. ",
                                            "uniqueName":  "/Lotus/Powersuits/Wraith/Abilities/WraithSowAbility",
                                            "imageName":  "WraithSow.png"
                                        },
                                        {
                                            "name":  "Gloom",
                                            "description":  "Summon a radial pulse wave that ensnares and slows enemies, siphoning their lifeforce for the Death Well. Allies within the wave steal health with each attack. ",
                                            "uniqueName":  "/Lotus/Powersuits/Wraith/Abilities/WraithGloomAbility",
                                            "imageName":  "WraithGloom.png"
                                        },
                                        {
                                            "name":  "Exalted Shadow",
                                            "description":  "When the Death Well fills, Sevagoth\u0027s Shadow form is ready to be released. Tear the enemy asunder with a collection of melee-focused abilities. ",
                                            "uniqueName":  "/Lotus/Powersuits/Wraith/Abilities/WraithReaperAbility",
                                            "imageName":  "WraithDontFearTheReaper.png"
